Name: DonutCrabs
About the game: Donut Crabs is a physics puzzle game. Control the platforms and guide the donut along the trajectory you set. Help the crab collect all the donuts on the island and solve the huge amount of relaxing and, sometimes, hard puzzles! Peculiarities: - Nice graphics. - Realistic physics. - Relaxing gameplay.
